        "publicTransport": "<p>The <a href=\"https://coomacoaches.com.au/snowy-mountains-bus-service/\" target=\"_blank\">Snowy Mountains Bus Service</a> will run from Jindabyne to Perisher and return every day during ski season.</p>",
