        "lastUpdated": 1782848641539,
        "otherAdvice": "<p><strong>Seasonal road closures:</strong></p><ul><li>Kosciuszko Rd between Perisher and Charlotte Pass,</li><li>Link Rd between Smiggin Holes and Guthega,</li><li>Kings Cross Rd between Cabramurra and Selwyn Resort, and</li><li>Tooma Rd and Snow Ridge Rd between Khancoban and Cabramurra.</li></ul><p><strong>Chains must be carried in Kosciuszko National Park in winter (4WD/AWDs exempt). </strong></p><p>All motorists should be prepared and equipped for sudden changes in road and weather conditions in Alpine area</p>",
